These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, pilot, accountant, videographer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, d&b, funk, techno
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, blend, bongani, montecristo
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, mystery, crime, animation
 1. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 2. the scientist is in an even position##4
 3. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 4. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the videographer##1
 5. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the pilot##1
 7. the blend-smoker is the accountant##1
 8. the person watching crime movies is in an even position##4
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is between the person watching animation movies and the fan of techno##2
10. the scientist is the person watching animation movies##1
11. the fan of funk is the videographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Job          | accountant  | scientist    | videographer    | pilot   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | ambient   | funk       | techno    |
| Cigar   | blend | davidoff | montecristo    | bongani |
| Movie-Genre           | mystery | animation       | fantasy | crime     |

