.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, old-henry, game, prince
4 different pets are kept: pony, dog, frog, goat
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, scientific, fantasy, crime
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, climbing, cycling, volleyball
 1. the owner of the goat is in an even position##4
 2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the owner of the dog is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 4. the old-henry-smoker is the person watching satire movies##1
 5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
 7. the prince-smoker is on the right of the game-smoker##1
 8. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left or far right##3
10. the game-smoker is in an odd position##4
11. the person watching fantasy movies is the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar          | bongani  | old-henry    | game     | prince       |
| Pet         | frog | goat | pony   | dog |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | satire   | scientific   | crime    |
| Sport         | cycling | volleyball  | biathlon | climbing   |

