.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, fonseca, vegafina, old-henry
City: paris, boston, miami, liverpool
There are 4 different nationalities: british, egyptian, indonesian, italian
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, white, ebony, azure
 1. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
 2. the egyptian is the person traveling to miami##1
 3. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the vegafina-smoker##3
 4. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
 5. the fonseca-smoker is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 6. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person who likes white##1
 7. the person who likes amber is the italian##1
 8. the person traveling to liverpool is in an even position##4
 9. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the british##1
10. the person who likes amber is the vegafina-smoker##1
11. the dunhill-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Cigar      | dunhill | vegafina   | old-henry    | fonseca      |
| City           | miami | paris | boston | liverpool     |
| Nationality   | egyptian      | italian   | british   | indonesian |
| Color           | azure         | amber       | ebony  | white       |

