.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, sprite, water
4 different games are played: scrabble, monopoly, poker, whist
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, bolivar, alhambra, bluemaster
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, bike, taxi, boat
 1. the person drinking fanta is the person playing scrabble##1
 2. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
 3. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
 4. the bolivar-smoker is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is the person driving the boat##1
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
 9. the person driving the taxi is the bolivar-smoker##1
10. the person driving the tram is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
11. the person drinking sprite is the person playing whist##1
12. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | water       | sprite   | fanta   | iced-tea   |
| Game       | monopoly        | whist | scrabble    | poker       |
| Cigar      | bluemaster | bolivar    | alhambra  | aristoff |
| Transport      | bike  | taxi  | tram | boat    |

