.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, chestnut, light-blue, black
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, bluemaster, dannemann, siglo
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, librarian, manager, musician
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, jet-ski, car, motorbike
 1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the dannemann-smoker is between the person driving the trike and the person who likes black##2
 3. the manager is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 4. the librarian is the person who likes apricot##1
 5. the bartender is on the left or right of the librarian##3
 6. the tiparillo-smoker is in an even position##4
 7. the person who likes chestnut is the bartender##1
 8. the dannemann-smoker is the librarian##1
 9. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
10. the librarian is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
11. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
12. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| Color    | light-blue    | black      | apricot          | chestnut    |
| Cigar   | bluemaster | siglo       | dannemann | tiparillo |
| Job     | musician     | manager      | librarian     | bartender |
| Transport   | jet-ski   | motorbike | car        | trike   |

