.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, swimming, ice-hockey, biathlon
There 4 different types of food: apple, artichoke, cauliflower, orange
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, january, june, december
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, biathloncher, dancer, project-manager
 1. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 2. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
 3. the person eating apple is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
 5. the person who's sport is cycling is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who's birthday is in december is between the dancer and the person who's birthday is in january##2
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is the person eating cauliflower##1
 8. the person who's sport is swimming is the person eating cauliflower##1
 9. the biathloncher is on the far right##1
10. the architect is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Sport      | ice-hockey  | swimming    | cycling       | biathlon       |
| Food          | orange    | cauliflower | artichoke | apple     |
| Birthday   | september | june        | december    | january   |
| Job   | architect  | dancer      | project-manager    | biathloncher |

