 6. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 8. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
 9. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3
10. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1
11. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3
12. the blend-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
