City: edinburgh, miami, marseilles, venice
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, egyptian, german, russian
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, chess, traveling, baking
 1. the person eating mango is on the right of the russian##1
 2. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
 3. the pakistani is between the person traveling to miami and the person who's hobby is chess##2
 4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the german##3
 6. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 7. the russian is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is the person traveling to miami##1
 9. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
11. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3
12. the egyptian is on the left of the person eating potato##1
13. the german is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Food          | garlic     | potato      | strawberry  | mango        |
| City   | miami     | marseilles | edinburgh | venice      |
| Nationality   | egyptian      | pakistani        | russian        | german        |
| Hobby         | baking | puzzles    | chess      | traveling |

