There 4 different types of food: asparagus, watermelon, pear, kiwi
City: colone, san-francisco, hamburg, liverpool
House: townhouse, wooden, cape-cod, gothic-revival
 1. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
 2. the cape-cod house is on the left of the townhouse house##1
 3. the person eating watermelon is between the gothic-revival house and the townhouse house##2
 4. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 5. the gothic-revival house is the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
 8. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 9. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
10. the person eating asparagus is in an even position##4
11. the person traveling to colone is the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |       3        |       4       |
| Beverage      | lemonade      | tea      | cola           | hot-chocolate |
| Food           | kiwi | watermelon | pear | asparagus        |
| City   | hamburg      | liverpool  | colone          | san-francisco      |
| House         | gothic-revival       | cape-cod    | townhouse       | wooden       |

