|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | lemonade   | soy-milk   | sprite     | water   |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | documentary       | drama | crime |
| House           | farmhouse     | cape-cod   | futuristic     | wooden     |
| City         | rome | marseilles | prague   | london |

