.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
City: berlin, hamburg, boston, miami
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, german, pakistani, canadian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, satire, sports, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, rock, hip-hop, techno
 1. the fan of rock is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
 2. the fan of techno is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
 3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is in an even position##4
 5. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 6. the pakistani is on the right of the canadian##1
 7. the german is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the italian##3
10. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
11. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
12. the italian is the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| City      | boston       | hamburg | berlin        | miami        |
| Nationality         | canadian | pakistani       | italian | german |
| Movie-Genre   | western     | satire        | mystery    | sports      |
| Music-Genre         | rock     | hip-hop    | techno | reggae   |

