.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, hiking, dancing, filmmaking
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, fanta, coffee, mirinda
4 different games are played: snooker, canasta, go, backgammon
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, helicopter, skateboard
 1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person playing go##1
 2. the person playing go is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking mirinda##2
 3. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
 4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 6. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person playing canasta##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
 8. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4
 9. the person playing canasta is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
10. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
11. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby   | hiking      | traveling | filmmaking     | dancing        |
| Beverage   | coffee | mirinda  | fanta     | tea |
| Game         | canasta    | snooker | go      | backgammon |
| Transport     | skateboard | car     | helicopter | bike       |

 